      <abstract id="aspace_da846b3b1021fa004db98499175648e8">The John Wolcott Papers document the revival of the historic Pinxter Festival in Albany, New York between 1972-1992.</abstract>
      <physloc id="aspace_7f9299cba47827a54f2d50bf1d04482f">The materials are located onsite in the department.</physloc>
